        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Neighborhood Noise Barriers Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill permits the use of funds out of the Highway Trust Fund to construct certain Type II noise barriers along federal-aid highways.</p> <p>The bill also makes the planning, design, or construction of such noise barriers eligible for surface transportation block grant program funding.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
